"""
""" Navigation
"""

""" insert mode

" (i) move to beginning of line
inoremap <C-e> <Esc>A
" (i) move to end of line
inoremap <C-a> <Esc>I
" (n) duplicate line
nnoremap <C-d> yyp

""" normal mode
" move in splits
nnoremap <C-J> <C-W><C-J>
nnoremap <C-K> <C-W><C-K>
nnoremap <C-L> <C-W><C-L>
nnoremap <C-H> <C-W><C-H>

" quick save
nnoremap <C-s> :update<CR>
nnoremap <Leader>x :x<CR>

